article_id:1683,category_name:News,title_name:Dragalia Lost Streaming Event Gift,image_path:,message:<div>To celebrate the 2nd anniversary of Dragalia Lost, a streaming event was hosted by the Japanese game live-streaming app Mirrativ began at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Because the event&#39;s goal of more than 500 Dragalia Lost streams was met, all players will receive a gift of 2,222,222 rupies!</div><div><br></div><div>The gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception. If the gift isn&#39;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1602223200,update_time1602223570